<div class = 'allcaps'><b>ENTER THE PHOTORAMA</b><br>ΦΩΤΟΣ (PHŌTOS)<br>GENITIVE OF ΦΩ͂ (PHŌS) LIGHT<br>ΓΡΑΦΗ (GRAPHÉ)<br>REPRESENTATION BY MEANS OF LINES" OR "DRAWING", TOGETHER MEANING DRAWING WITH LIGHT.<br>MODIFICATION OF - ORAMA FROM ANCIENT GREEK ὍΡᾹΜᾸ, (HÓRĀMA, “SIGHT, SPECTACLE”)</div>
